<div class="grid-2">
    <div>
        <p>Salgirah is a religious festival observed by Ismaili Muslims marking the birthday of their spiritual leader. His Highness the Aga Khan V was appointed the role of Imam to 15 million Ismailis worldwide in 2025. October 12 marked his first Salgirah.</p>
        <br>
        <p>The identity launched to over 1 million social media impressions across 21 countries in 10 languages. This was the fifth year working on the system — the global activation consistently demonstrates how a unified identity travels across unexpected materials and age groups.</p>
